				text: '<p>The friendly atmosphere during these two and a half days was essential to understanding how the community functions and especially how important it is to attend these meetings: not only to keep raising awareness for diversity, gender equality, and change, but it also serves as a reminder to why and how we volunteer for Love Foundation in the first place. This is why I loved asking for and listening to the stories of community members and how they came to become part of Love Foundation.</p>',
