				text: '<p>The amazing thing about this community is not only the different personalities but also how the pillars of the organization are mirrored in each of us, from those who are more connected to environmental protection issues, to those who are more interested in political dynamics. I strongly believe that this diversity of interests makes this community unique and meeting all these amazing people reminded me of why I decided to become part of this project originally.</p>',
