				created_by: 'd4d3d420-7bde-4afd-9295-683e6bd414bd',
				created_on: '2022-12-02T14:38:33.297Z',
				text: '<p>It is then no surprise that Love Foundation had a hub born out of this water crisis with the Cape Town hub being founded in 2019. The four founding members hit the ground running, organizing beautiful parties and yoga sessions, but hit a wall with the pandemic. However, our main partner, Viva con Aqua turned its sights to Cape Town and founded a branch in 2020. Along with this branch, Viva con Aqua opened Villa Viva, a multi-purpose guest house, networking platform and creative hub to be utilized by both Viva con Aqua team and the Love Foundation hubs. Thankfully by then, sufficient rain fall had provided the Cape Town region with plenty of water, avoiding the Day Zero catastrophe.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',
